# Vector Search

Vector search runs as a task in the data preparation workflow. The job is defined in [resources/data-preparation-resource.yml](../../resources/data-preparation-resource.yml) (task key `VectorSearchIndex`). It builds a vector index from the preprocessed data table using the `vector_search_endpoint` and `vector_search_index` bundle variables.

For setup and deployment, refer to [resources/README_agentops.md](../../resources/README_agentops.md).